---
import Photo from './Photo.astro';
import portrait from '../assets/photos/philosophy-portrait.jpg';
---

<section id="about" class="from-mist-light to-mist-dark bg-gradient-to-br">
  <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl grid-cols-1 items-start gap-10 px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-14 lg:px-10 lg:py-24">
    <!-- Black-and-white portrait, letterboxed on black like the source design -->
    <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-sm bg-black py-10 lg:col-span-5 lg:mt-16 lg:max-w-none" data-fade>
      <Photo
        src={portrait}
        alt="Black-and-white portrait of Dewa Patang"
        ratio="4/5"
        sizes="(min-width: 1024px) 40vw, 100vw"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="lg:col-span-7">
      <h2 class="font-display text-4xl tracking-wide uppercase sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl" data-fade>
        PHILOSOPHY
      </h2>

      <div class="mt-8 max-w-prose space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed sm:text-xl" data-fade>
        <p>
          Rooted in a multidisciplinary understanding of architecture, interiors, and
          craftsmanship, Dewa Kamin Interior Design creates spaces that enrich daily life while
          standing the test of time. At the heart of our practice is a commitment to designing
          environments that feel timeless, purposeful, and uniquely reflective of each client's
          aspirations.
        </p>
        <p>
          Inspired by nature, culture, innovation, and heritage, we create residential,
          commercial, hospitality, and retail environments that are both functional and
          inspiring. Every project is approached with care and creativity, balancing beauty,
          practicality, and a strong sense of place.
        </p>
        <p>
          Above all, we value the relationships built throughout the design process. Our goal is
          to create spaces that stand the test of time and experiences that are as meaningful as
          the finished result. Every project is an opportunity to create something lasting,
          distinctive, and deeply reflective of the people it serves.
        </p>
        <p>
          With passion and gratitude,<br />
          Dewa Patang
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
